FoCoCo – UI/UX Inspiration Summary

FoCoCo draws UI/UX inspiration from six top-tier apps, each contributing actionable ideas for different sections of the platform.

⸻

1. STRAVA

Focus: Social Fitness & Gamification
Key Features:
	•	Activity-centric UI with maps and performance stats
	•	Gamification (leaderboards, streaks)
	•	Clear performance metrics display

FoCoCo Actions:
	•	Log round UI for golf stats
	•	Visualize streaks/goals
	•	Engaging stats display in Mental Performance Index

⸻

2. OURA RING

Focus: Wellness via Biometric Insights
Key Features:
	•	Dashboard with holistic readiness score
	•	Clear visualizations of physiological data
	•	Personalized wellness guidance

FoCoCo Actions:
	•	Dashboard for Mental Performance Index
	•	AI Insight visualizations
	•	Premium, trusted design aesthetic

⸻

3. HEADSPACE

Focus: Mindfulness & Habit Building
Key Features:
	•	Animated, friendly UI
	•	Structured courses with streak tracking
	•	Daily engagement and check-ins

FoCoCo Actions:
	•	Coaching module breakdowns
	•	Friendly onboarding (e.g., VARK test)
	•	Daily nudges and streaks
	•	Explain abstract concepts visually

⸻

4. CALM

Focus: Serene Immersion & Wellness Content
Key Features:
	•	Nature-inspired visuals
	•	Organized content hubs
	•	Immersive audio playback

FoCoCo Actions:
	•	Serene UI for coaching/journaling
	•	Organized coaching module library
	•	Immersive module player
	•	Showcase premium features subtly

⸻

5. REVOLUT

Focus: Professionalism & Financial Clarity
Key Features:
	•	Clean, secure, minimal UI
	•	Clear subscription & account management
	•	Well-designed components & seamless nav

FoCoCo Actions:
	•	Clear subscription/AI token flows
	•	Professional profile/settings UI
	•	High polish and intuitive layout

⸻

6. DUOLINGO

Focus: Gamified Learning & Progress
Key Features:
	•	Skill tree/progression paths
	•	Badges, streaks, visual motivation
	•	Bite-sized learning with repetition

FoCoCo Actions:
	•	Coaching module path visualization
	•	Mental Index gamification
	•	Reward animations & progress feedback
